@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Air Transport Company Collaborator" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC

ATCC -> System : Requests to remove a pilot from company roster

activate System
System --> ATCC : Requests company and pilot identification
deactivate System

ATCC -> System : Provides company and pilot identification

activate System
System --> System : Check if collaborator is authorized
System --> System : Validate air transport company
System --> System : Check if collaborator belongs to company
System --> System : Validate pilot
System --> System : Check if pilot belongs to company
System --> System : Check if pilot is active
System --> System : Check if pilot has assigned flight plans

alt pilot can be made inactive
    System --> System : Make pilot inactive
    System --> ATCC : Pilot made inactive successfully
else pilot cannot be made inactive
    System --> ATCC : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate ATCC

@enduml